ğŸ“Œ Objective:

Parse an input file of date-value pairs and compute their value based on a historical Bitcoin price database. If an exact date isnâ€™t found, use the closest earlier date.
ğŸ› ï¸ Implementation Plan:

Files:

    main.cpp

    BitcoinExchange.hpp / .cpp

